esqlQuery.esql:
// Alert triggers when the used_logspace exceeds the recommended threshold value {90} within the look back time window.
// The alert is grouped by Server Name.
// You can adjust the threshold value by modifying the used_logspace in the WHERE clause. 
 FROM metrics-microsoft_sqlserver.transaction_log-default
| STATS used_logspace=MAX(mssql.metrics.used_log_space_pct) * 100
 by mssql.metrics.server_name
| WHERE used_logspace > 90
